Attempt to help Votersdaily an attempt to scrape the contents of government schedules and combine that event data into a single datastore. 
Lang: PHP 5.2.x
Author: Chauncey Thorn chaunceyt@gmail.com

NOTE: Work in progress!
CHANGELOG

08-15-2009 
- initial import of HouseSchedule.php parser - http://www.house.gov/house/House_Calendar.shtml
- initial import of HouseRollCallVotes.php parser - http://clerk.house.gov/evs/2009/index.asp
- initial import of SenateRollCallVotes.php parser - http://www.senate.gov/legislative/LIS/roll_call_lists/vote_menu_111_1.xml
- modified code so all parser(s) are executed by ScraperScheduler

08-16-2009
- initial import of SenateCalendar.php http://democrats.senate.gov/calendar/2009-08.html
- inital import of PresidentialActions.php http://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing_room/PresidentialActions/
- initial support for couchdb (using: http://wiki.apache.org/couchdb/Getting_started_with_PHP)

